      <h1 class="content-hero-title">Salvia Divinorum</h1>
      <p class="content-hero-subtitle">Salvia divinorum is one of the most unusual psychoactive plants known &mdash; its active compound, salvinorin A, is the most potent naturally occurring hallucinogen by weight and works through a mechanism entirely different from all other classic psychedelics. Its character is alien, disorienting, and genuinely unpredictable. It is not well-suited to recreational use.</p>
